{"tid":401761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無證移民勝利 紐約禁查居民身份","createTime":"2017-09-16T01:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T03:32:22.000Z","uid":89134,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc17dac81ef45fd258e8c4dda400f1e26e90efdd","tid":401761,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"有「庇護城市」之稱的紐約，州長科莫今日簽署行政命令，禁止州政府部門或官員，向任何人查詢其移民身份，以降低無證移民對被遺返的擔憂。科莫指，紐約之成功依賴來自四面八方的移民，不容政治問題或恐嚇在紐約作出分化。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n科莫今日簽署第170條行政命令，禁止政府人員向任何人查詢其移民身份。不過，如居民正申請政府服務或福利，或執法部門因刑事案件正進行調查，有關行政命令則不適用如此。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n科莫在聲明中表示，華府移民政策正不斷向後倒退，紐約州政府有責任保護移民，免於被聯邦政府以「莫須有」罪名針對。他續指，紐約成功建基於來自全球四面八方的移民，不容政治恐嚇分化紐約居民。（鄭柏齡／紐約報導）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170916/1204941/%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%E3%80%80%E7%B4%90%E5%B7%9E%E7%A6%81%E6%9F%A5%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170916%2F1204941%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2588%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B4%2590%25E5%25B7%259E%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD&d=PwBGKwisCUV%2FBu%2FFbY7d77%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=77e19a32\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170916/1204941/%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%E3%80%80%E7%B4%90%E5%B7%9E%E7%A6%81%E6%9F%A5%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD</a>"},{"pid":"91d0b89270f21d58a58b1cf187b9d51e21d8630f","tid":401761,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"點解偷渡非法移民變左合法咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bdac9129ffc6bb6ec7474910eb480bca0129a7","tid":401761,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:4